  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    uk.ac.ebi.ep.core.search.Config.getDomain(String)
    use ebeye-adapter's Domains enum
    uk.ac.ebi.ep.core.search.Config.getResultFields(Domain)
    This method is not used, as for every search in EB-Eye we retrieve either acc field (uniprot domain), or UNIPROT pseudo-field or id field (to get from it the acc of any uniprot references).
    uk.ac.ebi.ep.core.search.Config.loadCacheData()
    this method loads EB-Eye fields from a XML file included in ep-domain. Use ebeye-adapter's Domains enum instead.
    uk.ac.ebi.ep.core.search.Config.unmarshalConfigFile(InputStream)
    this method is only used by the deprecated Config.loadCacheData()
